  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/5b168cb4bf2df3de178f974e8a222fb9.poster.avif?t=1766177770\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/5b168cb4bf2df3de178f974e8a222fb9.webm?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/5b168cb4bf2df3de178f974e8a222fb9.mp4?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Braise</strong> is a narrative adventure game set in a fantastical universe. Play as a young woman investigating the disappearance of her grandmother and a dragon that has gone mad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the Dragon’s Valley and complete quests and puzzles to uncover the mysteries it holds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/75a53f076e5f3cad29bb24e339b350d1.poster.avif?t=1766177770\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/75a53f076e5f3cad29bb24e339b350d1.webm?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/75a53f076e5f3cad29bb24e339b350d1.mp4?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover an exciting story and its endearing characters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world where Dragons and Humans are living in a fragile peace, you follow the trail of your missing grandmother, a famous champion. While the calm of the valley is shaken by the madness of its dragon, a mysterious cult seems to be moving in the shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/2e272388338944b4cf1630ddb3647210.poster.avif?t=1766177770\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/2e272388338944b4cf1630ddb3647210.webm?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/2e272388338944b4cf1630ddb3647210.mp4?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To uncover all its secrets, you will need to thoroughly explore the valley!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the river to the temple, passing through the dungeon, the valley contains various locations teeming with items to find that will help you progress in the adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/f580339e45a85635160abdfe561fe187.poster.avif?t=1766177770\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/f580339e45a85635160abdfe561fe187.webm?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/f580339e45a85635160abdfe561fe187.mp4?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete the quests of the valley’s inhabitants and solve puzzles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ll need to use your logic and creativity to solve puzzles. Whether it’s combining objects or observing hidden clues in the environment, each puzzle immerses you deeper into this rich fantasy world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u></u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/77d8c73fe04cf52859364842cc2b23d2.poster.avif?t=1766177770\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/77d8c73fe04cf52859364842cc2b23d2.webm?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/77d8c73fe04cf52859364842cc2b23d2.mp4?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Look for bait and the best fishing spots to discover all the varieties of fish in the river!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The game offers an experience of approximately 1h30 to 2 hours.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >About the game:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Developed by a single person.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First project in video game development.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A one-year project.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-drawn pixel art, without AI.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/5b168cb4bf2df3de178f974e8a222fb9.poster.avif?t=1766177770\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/5b168cb4bf2df3de178f974e8a222fb9.webm?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/5b168cb4bf2df3de178f974e8a222fb9.mp4?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Braise</strong> is a narrative adventure game set in a fantastical universe. Play as a young woman investigating the disappearance of her grandmother and a dragon that has gone mad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the Dragon’s Valley and complete quests and puzzles to uncover the mysteries it holds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/75a53f076e5f3cad29bb24e339b350d1.poster.avif?t=1766177770\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/75a53f076e5f3cad29bb24e339b350d1.webm?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/75a53f076e5f3cad29bb24e339b350d1.mp4?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover an exciting story and its endearing characters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world where Dragons and Humans are living in a fragile peace, you follow the trail of your missing grandmother, a famous champion. While the calm of the valley is shaken by the madness of its dragon, a mysterious cult seems to be moving in the shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/2e272388338944b4cf1630ddb3647210.poster.avif?t=1766177770\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/2e272388338944b4cf1630ddb3647210.webm?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/2e272388338944b4cf1630ddb3647210.mp4?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To uncover all its secrets, you will need to thoroughly explore the valley!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the river to the temple, passing through the dungeon, the valley contains various locations teeming with items to find that will help you progress in the adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/f580339e45a85635160abdfe561fe187.poster.avif?t=1766177770\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/f580339e45a85635160abdfe561fe187.webm?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/f580339e45a85635160abdfe561fe187.mp4?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete the quests of the valley’s inhabitants and solve puzzles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ll need to use your logic and creativity to solve puzzles. Whether it’s combining objects or observing hidden clues in the environment, each puzzle immerses you deeper into this rich fantasy world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u></u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/77d8c73fe04cf52859364842cc2b23d2.poster.avif?t=1766177770\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/77d8c73fe04cf52859364842cc2b23d2.webm?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/77d8c73fe04cf52859364842cc2b23d2.mp4?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Look for bait and the best fishing spots to discover all the varieties of fish in the river!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The game offers an experience of approximately 1h30 to 2 hours.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >About the game:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Developed by a single person.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First project in video game development.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A one-year project.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-drawn pixel art, without AI.</p></li></ul>",
